				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: What level can we charm?<a name="70726"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Dec 7 04 5:00 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>I played with this song in RCoD, and I wasn't impressed.  Damage output on a charmed mob seems to be nerfed; anything I sicced a pet would own my pet.  In theory, you could swarm with it, but I found it more trouble than it is worth.  Most things that give exp these days summon.  Further, the headache of constantly mezzing both mobs, charming one, having it attack another, then redoing this all over when mez breaks is just irritating.
<br />

<br />
In addition to all of the soloing issues, the duration is variable, which I don't like for crowd control.  A solid 18 seconds of mez lockdown is much preferred.
<br />

<br />
The song could be useful if we got it at an earlier level, but once you get Vulka's, that will be your primary source of crowd control.  
<br />

<br />
</span></td>
